Title: 1 of these top non-QB prospects will be available for the Cardinals with 16th pick in draft
Description: The Arizona Cardinals have the 16th overall pick in the 2021 NFL draft. They could land any of a number of prospects. Who are the players who could be available? NFL.com’s Daniel Jeremiah released his latest rankings of the top 50 draft prospects and we know the Cardinals will be guaranteed to land a player in his top 16 if they want.
Author: USA Today on MSN.com
